_comm: Port to listen on. You may need root access if the value is less than 1024.
IP address to listen on. Change to "0.0.0.0" to listen on all network interfaces.
Tag of the inbound proxy. May be used for routing.
Settings of the protocol. Varies based on protocol.

sniffing._comm: Target domain will be overriden to the one carried by the connection, if the connection is HTTP or HTTPS.
